{"tid":886724,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果推出了一件僅售 9 美元的小配件！Android 用戶也跑來搶買！","createTime":"2018-11-02T10:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T13:25:25.000Z","uid":26418,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8ca37ac833988e2ece5e8582bc2a11b0f90ccc27","tid":886724,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:12:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/11/02/apple-usb-c-to-355-converter/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F11%2F02%2Fapple-usb-c-to-355-converter%2F&d=%2FwvC0QD7q%2Bc%2B2coBXKGRyZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=929b2048\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/11/02/apple-usb-c-to-355-converter/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有沒有想過 Apple 會推出一件只是 9 美元的小配件？它甚至吸引一些 Android 用戶來搶買？蘋果發佈最新的 iPad Pro，當中將 Lightning 改成 USB-C，而一些用戶使用 3.5mm 音源線耳機便要找 USB-C 轉 3.5mm 插口的轉換器。因此，Apple 推出自家 USB-C 轉 3.5mm 耳筒插口轉換器，售價只需 US$9（NT$ 290/HK$69)，在 Apple Online Store 訂更可以免費送貨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人測試過，能在 Pixel、Huawei P20 Pro、Essential Phone 等裝使用，效果很好。事實上，Google 也有推出同類轉換器，賣 US$12，而 Razer 則賣 US$20，相信賣 US$9 又能免費送貨的 Apple 轉換器會更受歡迎吧！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n產品名稱：USB-C 轉 3.5mm 耳筒插口轉換器<br />\n售價：HK$69 | NT$ 290<br />\n官方詳細資料：香港 | 台灣"},{"pid":"5108fa5c5d68cbb499c0636db794639782464c72","tid":886724,"uid":89514,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:17:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd80378b0b493aa4c70136c1af1f38984c8932c5","tid":886724,"uid":109383,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5108fa5c5d68cbb499c0636db794639782464c72","tid":886724,"uid":89514,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:17:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:20:34.000Z","msg":"事實上，Google 也有推出同類轉換器，賣 US$12，而 Razer 則賣 US$20<br />\n<br />\n唔見左唔可以買過條？"},{"pid":"b77389228b8e982cd1db2723c381052ed4fcd5b7","tid":886724,"uid":134415,"like":1,"dislik